ge-chart-17","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart#variants","content":"Color variants convey meaning at a glance — use `success`, `warning`, or `critical` alongside descriptive text."},"1298":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart-18","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart#label-type","content":"Control the font size of the primary label using `labelType`. Use `'value'` for numeric or percentage values and `'text'` for short descriptive strings."},"1299":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart-19","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart#gauge-not-sizing-correctly","content":"The component uses `container-type: inline-size` and fills its parent width. Ensure the parent has a defined width:"},"1300":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart-20","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/gauge-chart#value-out-of-range","content":"Values outside the valid range are clamped silently at runtime. For continuous mode the range is 0–100; for segmented mode the range is 0 to the segment count."},"1301":{"id":"/docs/components/layout/box","page_id":"/docs/components/layout/box","type":"page","content":"Box","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components","Layout"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/layout/box"},"1302":{"id":"/docs/components/layout/box-0","page_id":"/docs/components/layout/box","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/layout/box","content":"Polymorphic layout component providing consistent spacing, elevation, rounding, and self-alignment"},"1303":{"id":"/docs/components/layout/box-1","page_id":"/docs/components/layout/box","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/layout/box#installation","content":"Installation"},"1304":{"id":"/docs/components/layout/box-2","page_id":"/docs/co